A widow's cow was found killed on Thursday in Bulagu village of Budalang'i sub-location, Bunyala subcounty. The culprit left behind his clothes and other items at the scene.Ann Onyango, 34, said she was shocked to find one of her cows lying dead, its stomach swollen and all legs tightly tied together. She said the clothes are familiar and belong a person from the village. She did not name the suspect. Villagers condemned the incident.